There's Fade Right,
you can just fade it all up, Shrinking,

00:16:31.530 --> 00:16:33.490
Random Spin.

00:16:34.130 --> 00:16:37.490
So, just drop the fade right into
one of these effect bins here,

00:16:37.490 --> 00:16:40.640
and they all get applied
at the same time.

00:16:40.690 --> 00:16:43.850
So now we've got the
bubbles and the text,

00:16:43.880 --> 00:16:45.960
and it's pretty straightforward.

00:16:49.220 --> 00:16:56.210
Then we move on to the shaker,
which is a lot of people, you know,

00:16:56.210 --> 00:16:57.450
they just want to use their content.

00:16:57.650 --> 00:16:59.170
They don't want to spend
a lot of time editing,

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:02.240
so it's really nice to just have
an automatic way of creating

00:17:03.030 --> 00:17:05.400
some interesting edits and sound
effects and stuff like that.

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:07.100
So we've got a lot of
different modes here.

00:17:07.100 --> 00:17:09.420
We can kind of go to romantic
mode all the way up to,

00:17:09.540 --> 00:17:12.860
I think they call this tarot mode,
so let's try that one out.

00:17:12.910 --> 00:17:17.420
And so we'll just shake it,
and of course it takes a little time,

