what we're going to see is we're

00:21:53.500 --> 00:21:58.370
going to see this direction moving
over to other related industries.

00:21:58.510 --> 00:22:03.190
Airplanes, boats, that kind of stuff.

00:22:03.190 --> 00:22:03.190
It should be interesting
to watch it evolve.

